14 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1190.a of Title 21, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving fund
18 for the Oklahoma State Regents for Higher Education to be designated
19 the “Anti-Hazing Revolving Fund”. The fund shall be a continuing
20 fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall consist of
21 all monies received by the Oklahoma State Regents for Higher
22 Education from fines collected pursuant to Section 1190 of Title 21
23 of the Oklahoma Statutes provided for the purpose of hazing
24 education programs. All monies accruing to the credit of the fund
